<p class="ql-align-center">没有一顿火锅解决不了的问题，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果有，那就两顿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当脆爽的毛肚吸饱够味汤汁，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当细嫩的牛蛙裹上麻辣红油，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当肥美的牛肉散发勾人香气，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当方正的肉粒经历浮沉后问世……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201122/e5cfaaf198584548bacaddb94358e887.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">封印在内心的馋虫被完全勾引出来，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一口麻辣鲜爽，带劲得过瘾，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淋漓的畅快，太令人怀念啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一次，就请跟随雨小荷一起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一探济南的火锅江湖</strong></p>
<h1>1</h1>
<h1>火凤祥鲜货火锅</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">地道川渝风味，满足你的味蕾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201122/8bc479673d7347d9835b83f31dc25b7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
